                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Egan</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-01-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 17, 1891</hi>.</date> (Received January
                        19.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Revolted fleet about to blockade Valparaiso, Iquique, and other ports. I have
                    advised consuls to make strong protests. Squadron urgently needed for protection
                    of United States interests.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
